text: Jiří Černoch (born September 1, 1996) is a Czech professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing for HC Sparta Praha of the Czech Extraliga. Černoch made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with HC Sparta Praha during the 2015-16 Czech Extraliga season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:HC Sparta Praha players Category:Czech ice hockey centres Category:People from Klatovy
